        <comment xml:lang="en">0.019 ha/ha (4.24E-7 ha/kg Potato), calculated as the fraction of crop area treated with lime (9.45%, from state level estimated agricultural acres with pH &lt;6.1, Bruulsema T and Jones J D 2021)  / (5  years between applications, based on Bruulsema T and Jones J D 2021).
