          <unitName xml:lang="en">dimensionless</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">For potato, seeds are tubers (Tab 1.14, ecoinvent v2.2 report 15b). Composition data obtained from Potatoes, raw, skin, in (http://www.nal.usda.gov/fnic/foodcomp/search/). First, composition data were refered to 1 kg dry mass. Then, C-contents were calculated considering a C-content/dry mass of 46% in carbohydrates (including fibres), 53% in proteins and 75% in fats. All data from "Evolutionary and Biochemical Aspects", A.D. Kay and T. Vrede (in Global Ecology, 2010, Elsevier B.V., S.E. Jørgensen Ed.).</comment>
