        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">This exchange is an aggregate of proxies for applied pesticide(s) Metribuzin, Pymetrozine (2.229E-1 kg/ha {1,4,1,1,1}; 1.373E-2 kg/ha {1,4,1,1,1}, respectively).
