        <comment xml:lang="en">Phosphate runoff to surface water  0.227kg PO4/ha (5.091E-6: 0.E+0 kg PO4/ha from manure, 5.187E-2 kg PO4/ha from mineral fertilisers, and 1.75E-1 kg PO4/ha from leaching from arable landPhosphate runoff to surface water is calculated using the SALCA-P model (Prasuhn 2006) with an average leaching factor for arable lands and the amount of phosphate in any applied solid manure, liquid manure and mineral fertilisers, as implemented in the ecoinvent agricultural LCI tool (see Ecoinvent_Too_Model_Description_20191015.pdf). Does not incorporate state or county data on soils, slope or conservation drainage infrastructure. Calculated with the ecoinvent agricultural LCI tool. (0.E+0 kg PO4/ha from manure, 5.187E-2 kg PO4/ha from mineral fertilisers, and 1.75E-1 kg PO4/ha from leaching from arable land)</comment>
